What we do

About LMS Bot

LMS Bot runs a friendly, invite-only Last Man Standing competition following the English Premier League. Participants choose one team to win each round. We coordinate entries and send reminders via WhatsApp only to people who have opted in.

How it works

  • Invited players opt in to WhatsApp messages.
  • Before each round, we send fixtures and a reminder.
  • Players reply PICK <team> in WhatsApp to enter.
  • If no pick is received, a default may be assigned per the published rules.

WhatsApp Messaging Policy

  • Opt-in: We only message participants who have given us permission.
  • Opt-out: Reply STOP at any time to stop messages.
  • Message types: Service updates, reminders, and results for the LMS game only. No marketing.
  • Frequency: Typically 1–3 messages per gameweek.

Privacy

We collect only what we need to run the game: your name and WhatsApp phone number. We do not sell or share your data with third parties.

  • Controller: LMS Bot
  • Data stored: Name, phone number, picks history, lives remaining.
  • Retention: Up to 12 months for dispute resolution.
  • Your rights: Contact us to request access or deletion.

By participating you agree to these terms. This site is independent and not affiliated with the Premier League.
